title: SUNDAY SERMON: The Common Decency That Makes You An Uncommon Dominator, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO256
itunes:title: SUNDAY SERMON: The Common Decency That Makes You An Uncommon Dominator, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO256
description: Whatever ever happened to common decency? There are things that everybody used to know & do...how to treat one another, how to talk to one another, how to be a good person..that hardly anyone knows & does anymore. That's the bad news. The good news is that if YOU know & do these things, you'll be rare. You'll stand out. Having good manners & being a decent person will help you dominate.
